  "about": {
    "heading": "About",
    "text": "Genshin Impact is an open-world action RPG developed by HoYoverse that takes place in the fantasy world of Teyvat, a land shaped by elemental powers like Anemo, Pyro, Hydro, and Electro. Players explore vast regions, solve puzzles, fight enemies in real-time combat, and follow a story centered on the mysterious journey of the Traveler searching for their lost sibling. One of the game's standout features is its character-switching combat system, where players build teams of unique characters and combine elemental abilities for powerful reactions."
  },
